      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Basarios Buzzkill",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "Aw, man. Basarios again? *sigh*\r\nEvery time I get called out to hunt\r\nthose stupid rocks my weapons\r\njust bounce off and then they gas\r\nme! Way to kick a guy when he\u0027s\r\ndown... I\u0027d really appreciate it if\r\nwe could hunt \u0027em together!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Basarios",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Basarios rabat-joies",
        "Client": "Sieur Jae",
        "Description": "Je n\u0027arr\u00EAte pas d\u0027\u00EAtre envoy\u00E9\r\naux Plaines de sable pour\r\nchasser des Basarios. Mon arme\r\nrebondit toujours sur eux et\r\nleur gaz m\u0027\u00E9tourdit \u00E0 chaque fois.\r\nPourrais-tu me donner des\r\nconseils pour les vaincre ?",
        "Target": "Chasser 2 Basarios",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Stormo di Basarios",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "Continuano a chiamarmi nelle\r\nPiane sabbiose per cacciare\r\ndei Basarios. La mia arma ci\r\nrimbalza sopra e vengo messo\r\nin difficolt\u00E0 dai loro gas.\r\nPotresti mostrarmi il modo\r\nmigliore per affrontarli?",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Basarios",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Basarios-Spa\u00DFbremsen",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "Oh Mann, schon wieder Basarios?\r\n*seufz* Jedes Mal, wenn ich die\r\njage, prallen meine Waffen von\r\ndenen ab! Das geht mir so auf\r\ndie Nerven! ... K\u00F6nnen wir die\r\nvielleicht zusammen jagen?",
        "Target": "Erjage zwei Basarios.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Basarios rocach\u00F3n",
        "Client": "Jae",
        "Description": "Vaya, \u00BFotra vez un Basarios?\r\nCada vez que me mandan a\r\ncazar a uno de esos rocachones,\r\nmis armas rebotan en ellos como\r\nsi nada, \u00A1y luego me gasean!\r\nOye... \u00A1me har\u00EDas un gran favor\r\nsi pudieras venir conmigo!",
        "Target": "Caza 2 Basarios",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0430 \u043D\u0430 \u0411\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043E\u0441\u0430",
        "Client": "\u0421\u0438\u0440 \u0414\u0436\u0435\u0439",
        "Description": "\u041C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0443\u0436\u0435 \u043A\u043E\u0442\u043E\u0440\u044B\u0439 \u0440\u0430\u0437 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u044F\u0442\r\n\u0432\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0411\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043E\u0441\u0430 \u0432\r\n\u041F\u0435\u0441\u0447\u0430\u043D\u044B\u0445 \u0440\u0430\u0432\u043D\u0438\u043D\u0430\u0445. \u041C\u043E\u0435 \u043E\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0438\u0435\r\n\u0438\u0445 \u043D\u0435 \u0431\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0442, \u0430 \u0438\u0445 \u0433\u0430\u0437 \u043B\u0438\u0448\u044C\r\n\u0434\u043E\u0431\u0430\u0432\u043B\u044F\u0435\u0442 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0431\u043B\u0435\u043C. \u041F\u043E\u043A\u0430\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C,\r\n\u043A\u0430\u043A \u0441 \u043D\u0438\u043C\u0438 \u0434\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F? \u0427\u0442\u043E\u0431\u044B \u044F\r\n\u0431\u044B\u043B \u0433\u043E\u0442\u043E\u0432 \u0432 \u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0443\u044E\u0449\u0438\u0439 \u0440\u0430\u0437.",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C 2 \u0411\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043E\u0441\u043E\u0432",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
